metadata.title: Disney Minnie Mouse Fleece Pullover Hoodie and Pants Outfit Set Infant to Toddler
features: Officially licensed Disney infant girls cute, comfy and stylish long sleeve graphic hooded sweatshirt and matching pants

Pull on closure; Sleeve cuffs for a better fit; Comfortable hood lining; Soft hand screen print design; Cuffed for a better fit; Drawstring closure; Functional pockets; Ankle cuffs for a better fit; Elastic waist for better fit
Durable and long-lasting hooded sweatshirt and pants set; made to be the essential cozy winter outfit for your athletic child with stylish and playful character designs
Youth fashion apparel made from soft clothing material that is safe for kid's skin; activewear with a comfortable fit that children can easily get dressed in every morning
Perfect for birthday gift, every day wear, Christmas holiday gift, outdoor play and cold weather
description: Your little girl is ready for a day filled with Disney magic in this stylish Minnie Mouse outfit. This warm and cozy hoodie and jogger pants set features cute artwork of the polka-dot loving and mouse-eared Minnie wearing her fashionable bow. Made from a soft material that keeps your kid comfortable, this adorable Minnie Mouse set is the perfect outfit for a fun day of play.
